# Cura to Slic3r profile conversion

> automatic tool to convert Cura slicing profile to Slic3r

## Install

clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ra100/curaToSlic3rProfile
cd curaToSlic3rProfile
python setup.py install
```

or use pip to install direclty from repo

```bash
pip install git+https://github.com/ra100/curaToSlic3rProfile
```

## Usage

```bash
cura2slic3r cura.ini slic3r.ini
```